      "text_html": "<p>[SceneModel(scene<em>id='54cc4b9b-9555-4042-9ee9-c6d05a1b6ff5', issue</em>id='77fb926f-d068-45da-a96f-c2e835876ebc', series<em>id='3e3fdb21-8f39-42ff-add7-6fbdda798a21', story</em>id=None, name='Deliberate Choice', story='At dawn outside the shrine, elders and wardens arrive and hold judgment over Squonk for desecrating the sacred place. Rugor gives a truthful account that condemns him on actions, then insists intent and consequence matter\u2014and that his blundering interference bought the time needed to understand the prison and stop the Ash Company. The elders refuse that reasoning and offer Rugor an honorable compromise if she steps aside; Rugor rejects it, removes her guardian torque, and resigns rather than participate in injustice. She walks away down Blackstone Pass, silently taking the heaviest load from Squonk\u2019s bursting pack and matching pace beside him\u2014choosing compassion over office and beginning their partnership.', style<em>id='vintage-four-color', scene</em>number=6, setting<em>id='shrine-aftermath-road', setting</em>shot<em>id=None, time</em>of<em>day='dawn', mood='Cold, formal judgment in pale light; then quiet resolve and bittersweet tenderness on the road.', cast=[CharacterRef(series</em>id='3e3fdb21-8f39-42ff-add7-6fbdda798a21', character<em>id='425c080d-ea71-4941-870d-7326b4d1f588', variant</em>id='331296d6-883d-417b-928c-747d6064e84c'), CharacterRef(series<em>id='3e3fdb21-8f39-42ff-add7-6fbdda798a21', character</em>id='6a337a36-8dc6-46af-a3dd-484a0593dcd1', variant_id='5214107a-27d4-47ae-b780-0c6d24c82f86')], pr</p>\n",
