        "text_html": "<p>Create a new setting named 'Dropcastle' from this reference image: <img src=\"data/dnd-nerds-comics/series/3e3fdb21-8f39-42ff-add7-6fbdda798a21/uploads/f506e971-DropCastle.png\" alt=\"reference\" />.  Use it as the master background.</p>\n",
