        "text_html": "<p>I would like to create a new publisher called \"Mythforge\".   Myth forge specializes in YA to Adult comics that take classic epics like the illad or beowulf and turn them into modern, or futuristic dramas.    Can you help me flesh out the description of the publishing house?</p>\n",
