        "text_html": "<p>The panel you mean is <strong>Scene 1: \u201cPass Tracks\u201d \u2014 Panel 6, \u201cNo Blood, No Bodies\u201d</strong> (beat: <em>\u201cRugor registers the absence of blood as the key clue.\u201d</em>).</p>\n\n<p>It\u2019s currently <strong>unrendered</strong>. Rendering Scene 1 (which includes that panel) will render <strong>13 panels</strong> total.</p>\n\n<p>Estimated cost: <strong>\u2248 $2.60</strong>.</p>\n\n<p>Confirm you want me to render <strong>Scene 1</strong> now? (yes/no)</p>\n",
