      {
        "name": "Tool Output",
        "text_html": "<p>[Outfit(outfit<em>id='comfort-shift-&amp;-sandals', series</em>id='3e3fdb21-8f39-42ff-add7-6fbdda798a21', name='Comfort shift &amp; sandals', description='A comfortable off-duty outfit for Rugor: a simple sleeveless linen shift that falls to mid-calf, cut loose for ease of movement. The fabric is unbleached oat-beige with slightly darker seams and visible hand-stitching; the hem is a little frayed and dust-stained from travel.\\n\\nSimple leather sandals with wide straps and a flat sole, worn and softened, with scuffed toes and darkened edges from mud and road grit. No jewelry or armor pieces\u2014just practical, restful clothing.', images={'vintage-four-color': 'data/dnd-nerds-comics/series/3e3fdb21-8f39-42ff-add7-6fbdda798a21/outfits/comfort-shift-&amp;-sandals/images/3eab1780-69ac-468e-bdc0-5122442f97a9.png'}, origin=None)]</p>\n",
