    "/publishers/i-do-it": [
      {
        "name": "You",
        "text_html": "<p>tell me about the publisher</p>\n",
        "sent": true
      },
      {
        "name": "the Editor",
        "text_html": "<p>\u201cI do it\u201d is positioned as a publisher of heartwarming, nostalgic family-life comics, with the core promise being: everyday parenting and household moments, told with humor that stays gentle enough to be \u201cfor all ages.\u201d The current description leans hard on relatability\u2014small incidents, kid-raising chaos, and the push-pull of family dynamics\u2014framed to land as both funny and emotionally warm rather than sharp or cynical.</p>\n\n<p>One critique: the description is generic enough that it doesn\u2019t yet tell me what this publisher will <em>not</em> publish (for example: satire, darker autobiographical work, teen/YA drama, or adult comedy). What tone is explicitly off-limits for \u201cI do it\u201d?</p>\n",
        "sent": false
      },
      {
        "name": "the Background Artist",
        "text_html": "<p>\ud83c\udfa8 <strong>master background \u2014 Joey's Bedroom in Watercolor (landscape)</strong> \u2014 done (1/1).</p>\n",
        "sent": false
      },
      {
        "name": "the Background Artist",
        "text_html": "<p>\ud83d\uddbc\ufe0f That's the batch: 1 rendered.</p>\n",
        "sent": false
      }
    ],
    "/series/joey": [
      {
        "name": "You",
        "text_html": "<p>Create a new setting named 'Joey's Bedroom'.  Description: Simple bedroom backdrop.    Bed with solid covered duvet, toy chest, window looking out to sky.  Then render a master background for it.</p>\n",
        "sent": true
      },
      {
        "name": "Tool Output",
        "text_html": "<p>SERIES BIBLE for joey</p>\n\n<p>CHARACTERS (cast with these exact ids):\n* Mum \u2014 character<em>id=mum\n    - variant 'holiday' \u2014 variant</em>id=6387347a-4909-4e90-a0c6-6b917161aa06 (sheets: childlike-crayon, watercolor)\n    - variant 'base' \u2014 variant<em>id=3ad3be20-d573-468d-9ec2-b8820efab768 (sheets: watercolor, 13e69e9c-46c7-4c7b-8fed-ebd1f0331c62)\n* Dog \u2014 character</em>id=dog\n    - variant 'Base' \u2014 variant<em>id=base (sheets: watercolor)\n* Joey \u2014 character</em>id=joey\n    - variant 'Base' \u2014 variant<em>id=base (sheets: watercolor)\n* Squirrel \u2014 character</em>id=f180355f-a958-4765-977c-4320e0e41270\n    - variant 'Base' \u2014 variant_id=8f7fb4bd-d7b8-413f-b55f-f1aaa17bfac7 (sheets: watercolor)</p>\n\n<p>SETTINGS (set scenes with these exact ids):\n* Backyard fence area \u2014 setting_id=fc5f21ba-eb8d-494c-9570-6c5b8da20c70 (masters: watercolor)</p>\n\n<p>STYLES:\n* Childlike Crayon \u2014 style<em>id=childlike-crayon\n* Conte Crayon \u2014 style</em>id=conte-crayon\n* Vintage Four Color \u2014 style<em>id=vintage-four-color\n* Monet-Inspired Impressionism \u2014 style</em>id=13e69e9c-46c7-4c7b-8fed-ebd1f0331c62\n* Stained Glass \u2014 style<em>id=stained-glass\n* Concept Sketch \u2014 style</em>id=concept-sketch\n* Origami Comic Style \u2014 style<em>id=origami\n* Van Gogh \u2014 style</em>id=van-gogh\n* Modern Anime \u2014 style<em>id=modern-anime\n* Hyper Realism \u2014 style</em>id=hyper-realism\n* Saturday Morning Cartoon \u2014 style<em>id=saturday-morning\n* Watercolor \u2014 style</em>id=watercolor</p>\n",
        "sent": false
      },
      {
        "name": "Tool Output",
        "text_html": "<p>setting<em>id=\"joey's-bedroom\" series</em>id='joey' name=\"Joey's Bedroom\" description='Simple child\u2019s bedroom interior, cozy and uncluttered. A single bed sits against one wall with a smooth, solid-color duvet neatly pulled up and a single pillow; the bedframe is simple wood. Near the foot of the bed is a low wooden toy chest with a hinged lid, lightly scuffed from use. One window on the back wall shows a clear view of open sky (no visible buildings), with simple curtains pulled to the sides. Soft, even daylight fills the room; light, warm wall color; plain floor with a small rug near the bed.' interior=True props=[Prop(name='single bed', description='Simple wooden single bed with a smooth, solid-color duvet (no pattern) and one pillow; neatly made.'), Prop(name='toy chest', description='Low wooden toy chest with hinged lid; lightly scuffed edges; sits near the bed.'), Prop(name='window', description='Rectangular window with simple frame and curtains; view looks out to open sky.'), Prop(name='small rug', description='Small oval or rectangular rug beside the bed; muted color, minimal pattern.')] origin=None images={} images_stale=[] shots=[]</p>\n",
        "sent": false
      },
      {
        "name": "the receipts",
        "text_html": "<p>\ud83c\udd95 <strong>Create setting</strong> \u2014 Joey's Bedroom, True</p>\n",
        "sent": false
      },
      {
        "name": "the Editor",
        "text_html": "<p><em>(That finished without words \u2014 the receipts above are what actually happened.  Say <strong>go on</strong> if there's more to do.)</em></p>\n",
        "sent": false
      }
    ],
