      {
        "name": "Tool Output",
        "text_html": "<p>Updated description to 'Portrait panel, inked rough take with NO setting/background plate and NO characters: a mostly white field with a single focal clue\u2014an irregular, dark, muddy smear/patch occupying the lower third of frame, slightly off-center. Indicate the smear\u2019s wet, gritty texture with feathered ink hatching and a few stippled grains; a faint, broken outline suggests uneven stone beneath the mud but keep it minimal so it reads as \u201cnot blood.\u201d Add a single short fingertip swipe mark through the patch (a lighter streak cutting across the dark tone), implying a test-wipe happened moments ago. No other environment, no hands, no boots, no shadows; let the negative space sell the isolation of the clue.' for Panel with ID '{'series<em>id': '3e3fdb21-8f39-42ff-add7-6fbdda798a21', 'issue</em>id': '77fb926f-d068-45da-a96f-c2e835876ebc', 'scene<em>id': 'a4ba2802-20c1-442e-8453-ee3e81d1d501', 'panel</em>id': '6e447a46-229f-4b14-97f9-f0661fa2c5cc'}'.</p>\n",
