    "/publishers/226b4d80-482c-48c3-9e09-0eca1350fe8a": [
      {
        "name": "You",
        "text_html": "<p>I would like to create a logo for this publisher.   It should look like a highly stylelized phoeinix rising from the smoke and ashes of a forge or furnace.   Help me flesh out the description please by asking me relevant questions that would help clarify the design.</p>\n",
        "sent": true
      },
      {
        "name": "the Editor",
        "text_html": "<p>Do you want the phoenix to read as <strong>mythic and solemn</strong> (epic rebirth) or <strong>industrial and aggressive</strong> (spark, steel, furnace violence)?</p>\n",
        "sent": false
      },
      {
        "name": "You",
        "text_html": "<p>epic rebirth, but definitely as something new and modern.   Rebirth and evolution.    Does that make sense?</p>\n",
        "sent": true
      },
      {
        "name": "the Editor",
        "text_html": "<p>Yes. One design decision will lock that in:</p>\n\n<p>Should the phoenix be built from <strong>smooth, geometric \u201cfuture\u201d shapes</strong> (clean vector-like curves, minimal feather detail) or from <strong>forged, blade-like facets</strong> (angular, shard/armor geometry) to signal \u201cevolution through fire\u201d?</p>\n",
        "sent": false
      },
      {
        "name": "You",
        "text_html": "<p>Think minimal.   Picaso's bull.</p>\n",
        "sent": true
      },
      {
