      },
      {
        "name": "the Editor",
        "text_html": "<p>Rendered the Mythforge logo reference image here:</p>\n\n<p><code>data/mythforge-comics/publishers/226b4d80-482c-48c3-9e09-0eca1350fe8a/images/05d1066c-ebd5-4764-a1e0-95bf2bbb5256.png</code></p>\n\n<p>One question: do you want the orange/red spiral to read more like a <strong>thin ember filament</strong> or a <strong>clearly visible helix</strong> at small sizes?</p>\n",
