        "name": "the Editor",
        "text_html": "<p>Heorot Run<br />\nConjunction Night<br />\nBayden Wolf<br />\nWolf at Heorot<br />\nBlack Conjunction<br />\nThe Hall in Darkness<br />\nGrendel Protocol<br />\nBinary Nightfall<br />\nThe Mercenary of Heorot<br />\nWulfcall</p>\n",
        "sent": false
