        "text_html": "<p>Updated description to 'The first engineered hunter-organism spawned on Heorot during conjunction night: fast, precise, and adapted to exploit the colony\u2019s routines and blind zones. It is terrifying enough to be misnamed as \u201cpredation,\u201d but its behavior suggests purpose\u2014an organism shaped to target settlements like this one.' for CharacterModel with ID '{'character<em>id': '6b2c7f35-fb11-4106-b44d-5926c76b9694', 'series</em>id': '9eea770b-f7f3-429b-b9a1-22beb98e6efe'}'.</p>\n",
        "sent": false
