      {
        "name": "the Character Designer",
        "text_html": "<p>I don\u2019t understand. What does \u201cbase variant\u201d mean here\u2014are you telling me to <strong>edit the base variant</strong> to lock in the <strong>4 arms + opposable claw pairs</strong> details?</p>\n\n<p>If yes, say: \u201cyes, update base variant,\u201d and answer one thing: <strong>are the four arms equal-sized, or is one pair smaller/secondary?</strong></p>\n",
