        "text_html": "<p>\u2702\ufe0f removed the background from the table</p>\n",
        "sent": true
      },
      {
        "name": "You",
        "text_html": "<p>The brief for this panel is a bit thin to rough well. Let's flesh it out together so the cast can be posed and the setting dressed.  Specifically, what is missing: Where the panel takes place (what cover the merchant is leaning out from, and what environment/background we see).; Who the merchant is (identity/species/look) and whether Squonk is present or not.; Basic shot framing/camera angle (e.g., waist-up two-shot, over-the-shoulder from Rugor, etc.)..</p>\n",
        "sent": true
      },
      {
        "name": "the Penciller",
        "text_html": "<p>We can\u2019t flesh it out yet because those three items are genuinely undefined in the panel as it stands, and I won\u2019t invent them. I need one concrete answer for each:</p>\n\n<p>1) <strong>Place / cover:</strong> What is the merchant leaning out from\u2014<strong>a wagon</strong>, <strong>a rock outcrop</strong>, <strong>a broken cart</strong>, <strong>a tent flap</strong>, <strong>a roadside ditch</strong>, or something else? And what do we see behind them (trees, cliff wall, pass road, snow, etc.)?</p>\n\n<p>2) <strong>Merchant identity + Squonk:</strong> Who is the merchant (name or at least <strong>species + distinctive look</strong>)? And <strong>is Squonk in this panel: yes or no</strong>?</p>\n\n<p>3) <strong>Shot framing:</strong> Pick one: <strong>waist-up two-shot</strong>, <strong>wide shot with the kids visible under the blanket</strong>, or <strong>over-the-shoulder from Rugor toward the merchant</strong>. Which?</p>\n\n<p>Answer those three and I\u2019ll update the panel beat/description, cast it, set the scene setting/props, pose figures, and render a take.</p>\n",
        "sent": false
      },
      {
        "name": "You",
        "text_html": "<p>The merchant is underneath a blanket where he hs been hiding.   They are underneath an overturned wagon.   The merchant is a human, and we don't yet have a character model for this.   Squonk is not in ths panel.    The shot narrow shot slightly above eye level of the merchant.</p>\n",
        "sent": true
      },
      {
        "name": "Tool Output",
