      {
        "name": "Tool Output",
        "text_html": "<p>[Setting(setting<em>id='blackstone-pass-road', series</em>id='3e3fdb21-8f39-42ff-add7-6fbdda798a21', name='Blackstone Pass Road', description='High mountain pass road carved into dark basalt cliffs; narrow switchback trail with sheer drop on one side and jagged rock wall on the other. Morning fog pools low and curls around stone outcrops; wet stones glisten, scattered scree and scrub pine cling to cracks. The road surface is packed dirt and gravel with occasional flat stone slabs; plenty of readable ground for ruts, boot prints, and broken arrow shafts. Palette: slate gray, cold greens, muted browns; ravens as small silhouettes in the distance. Strong sense of verticality and wind.', interior=False, props=[Prop(name='overturned wagon', description='Splintered wooden merchant wagon on its side, one wheel bent; canvas tarp half-torn; forms a makeshift barricade with crates and sacks wedged beneath. Fresh scrape marks in the dirt where it was dragged into place.'), Prop(name='arrow shafts', description='Two or three broken arrow shafts with crude fletching, snapped near impact; scattered among boot prints.'), Prop(name='deep ruts', description='Twin wagon ruts gouged into damp soil, with clumped mud thrown outward; indicates heavy load.')], origin=None, images={'vintage-four-color': 'data/dnd-nerds-comics/series/3e3fdb21-8f39-42ff-add7-6fbdda798a21/settings/blackstone-pass-road/images/5cd1ce12-e1fe-40f1-b587-07029d1439c2.png'}, images<em>stale=[], shots=[]), Setting(setting</em>id='80460ca0-f</p>\n",
