        "name": "Tool Output",
        "text_html": "<p>Updated description to 'Narrow landscape panel, camera slightly above the merchant\u2019s eye level, looking down into the cramped hiding space under an overturned wagon.</p>\n\n<p>Foreground/near-mid: the wagon\u2019s broken underside dominates the top of frame\u2014splintered boards, axle beam, and a bent wheel rim silhouetted; torn canvas and dangling harness straps create a low ceiling.</p>\n\n<p>Under the wagon: the merchant (human, unmodeled NPC) is mostly hidden under a heavy blanket; only his tense face and one hand are visible as he lifts the blanket edge to look out. His eyes are wide, jaw tight; dirt and sweat on his skin.</p>\n\n<p>Midground right: Rugor is crouched/knelt just outside the wagon\u2019s edge, kept to a partial profile so we read his open, low hands and steady posture without stealing focus. He maintains respectful distance, not reaching in.</p>\n\n<p>Background sliver: the Blackstone Pass road\u2014wet gravel, ruts, and cold fog\u2014visible as a narrow wedge beyond Rugor, keeping the world present but secondary.</p>\n\n<p>Children remain under the blanket as indistinct small shapes; only a hint of small hands gripping fabric near the merchant\u2019s shoulder. No Squonk in frame. Leave clean negative space near upper left for lettering.' for Panel with ID '{'series<em>id': '3e3fdb21-8f39-42ff-add7-6fbdda798a21', 'issue</em>id': '77fb926f-d068-45da-a96f-c2e835876ebc', 'scene<em>id': 'a4ba2802-20c1-442e-8453-ee3e81d1d501', 'panel</em>id': '9ec40f26-e42f-47cb-9c6c-ee9b4402232e'}'.</p>\n",
